  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Aircon Installation Site Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope / Responsibilities:</strong></p><ol><li><p>Lead and manage a team of 5–8 aircon installation technicians.</p></li><li><p>Plan and coordinate installation schedules to meet project deadlines.</p></li><li><p>Perform and supervise installation of air conditioning units, including indoor and outdoor units, piping, wiring, and testing.</p></li><li><p>Ensure all installations comply with safety standards, company procedures, and manufacturer specifications.</p></li><li><p>Troubleshoot and resolve on-site technical issues efficiently.</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper documentation of work done, including installation reports and maintenance logs.</p></li><li><p>Be ready to respond to urgent assignments or on-call situations (MC readiness).</p></li></ol><p><strong>Requirements / Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Experience in air conditioning installation and maintenance.</p></li><li><p>Leadership experience or ability to manage a team.</p></li><li><p>Ability to work under pressure and commit to urgent schedules.</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of safety procedures and standards.</p></li></ul>",
